description.text:
This stepped cylinder allows you to check 4 outside diameters in the X and Y directions, and 4 heights in the Z direction.  Diameters ore 1.00&quot;, 0.75&quot;, 0.50&quot;, and 0.25&quot;.  Heights are 0.25&quot;, 0.50&quot;. 0.75&quot;, and 1.00&quot;  
The top surfaces of the cylinders are inscribed with lines.  Line these up with the positive X and Y axes so you can keep track of them after the print is removed from the printer.  
It is designed with a brim so it won't lift off of the build platform.  The brim doesn't interfere with the measurements, but I usually trim it off anyway.
